room_title: Escape room "Disease X" by Locked A Rochester Escape Room in Rochester (NY)
room_address: 200 Buell Rd suite A-8 Rochester, NY 14624
room_description: A deadly virus has swept across the globe four scientists in Rochester New York have found the antidote which can save mankind however their lab has been contaminated and they didn’t survive. You and your team must retrace the scientists foot steps in hopes to save the human race. You only have one hour in the lab until the virus claims it’s next victim.
